PN,34501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FWatch Live: Donna Ockenden reveals
OL,8,Fscale of maternity failings affecting
OL,9,Fmore than 2,500 cases
OL,11,FMore than 500 mothers and babies
OL,12,Fsuffered potentially avoidable harm or
OL,13,Fdied at a "toxic" hospital trust, a
OL,14,Fdamning report has revealed.
OL,16,FThe biggest maternity review in NHS
OL,17,Fhistory has exposed 162 deaths -
OL,18,Fincluding 156 children and six mothers
OL,19,F- could have been avoided if they were
OL,20,Fgiven better care.
OL,26,@uD@KOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThe Ockendon report, an independent
OL,8,Finquiry into maternity services in
OL,9,FNottingham, has included the cases of
OL,10,F2,500 families over a 20-year period,
OL,11,Fand serious and deadly incidents in
OL,12,Fmaternity care and found a string of
OL,13,F"repeated failures".
OL,15,FFamilies of babies who died or were
OL,16,Fleft seriously disabled due to
OL,17,Fmistakes at Nottingham University
OL,18,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) have
OL,19,Freceived the final report of the
OL,20,Findependent inquiry today.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThe report's purpose is to give a
OL,8,Fvoice to the families who suffered,
OL,9,Fprovide answers as to why their care
OL,10,Fwasn't good enough, expose systemic
OL,11,Fand cultural failings in the NUH and
OL,12,Fto change maternity care nationally.
OL,14,FOverall, 520 mothers and babies
OL,15,Fsuffered potentially avoidable harm,
OL,16,Fwith 162 of them dying after
OL,17,Fexperiencing substandard care.
OL,19,FSome 94 still births, 62 neonatal
OL,20,Fdeaths and the deaths of six mums were
OL,21,Faffected by substandard care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FLife-long injuries
OL,9,FSome of the babies and mothers who
OL,10,Faren't included in the number who died
OL,11,Fstill suffered life-long injuries,
OL,12,Fboth physical and psychological.
OL,14,FThe team found failures in the care of
OL,15,Fthe babies after they were born that
OL,16,Fled to permanent neurological
OL,17,Fdisorders like cerebral palsy.
OL,19,FBabies also suffered serious brain
OL,20,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThey examined a series of cases where
OL,8,Fa Hypoxic Ischaemic Encephalopathy (an
OL,9,Finjury caused by a lack of oxygen to
OL,10,Fthe brain) was recorded. It found 50%
OL,11,Fof them could have been avoided with
OL,12,Fbetter care.
OL,14,FBut there was also long-term harm done
OL,15,Fto mothers.
OL,17,FOut of the 115 cases where mothers
OL,18,Fsuffered catastrophic blood loss, 26%
OL,19,Fwere avoidable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FMany mothers also suffered
OL,8,Fpsychologically; of the mothers who
OL,9,Freported severe psychological trauma,
OL,10,F75% of them were found to have had
OL,11,Fsuboptimal care.
OL,13,FNationally, a parliamentary committee
OL,14,Fhas found that 33% of women experience
OL,15,Fbirth trauma on average.
OL,17,FA toxic culture
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FSome 800 members of staff at the
OL,8,Ftrust, some of whom are still there
OL,9,Fand others who aren't, were asked to
OL,10,Fprovide input to the inquiry.
OL,12,FThe majority were midwives, but a
OL,13,Flarge number of obstetricians and
OL,14,Fother medical staff were interviewed
OL,15,For filled in the online survey.
OL,17,FThe report exposes a failure to staff
OL,18,Fmaternity services properly and a
OL,19,Fculture of bullying.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FAlmost 90% of those asked said they
OL,8,Fdidn't feel they had enough staff to
OL,9,Fdo their job properly.
OL,11,FMore than 40% had either witnessed or
OL,12,Fpersonally experienced bullying by
OL,13,Fmanagers or other colleagues on a
OL,14,Fregular basis.
OL,16,FThe top issues raised about management
OL,17,Fwere that they were:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThe review attempted to highlight many
OL,8,F"positive accounts" that patients gave
OL,9,Fof staff. It praised their "compassion
OL,10,Fand skill".
OL,12,F58% of people asked said that people
OL,13,Fsupport each other and work as a team.
OL,14,FMore than half felt that staff were
OL,15,Factively taking steps to improve
OL,16,Fsafety.
OL,18,FIt lays the service's failings firmly
OL,19,Fat the feet of the system, whose
OL,20,Ffundamental flaws, it argues, let down
OL,21,Feveryone involved.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThe mother's stories
OL,9,FOne of the report's intentions was to
OL,10,Fprovide a space for mothers' testimony.
OL,12,FThe families were the "driving force"
OL,13,Fbehind the review, with the Hawkins
OL,14,Ffamily credited as one of "the
OL,15,Fcourageous group... who have endured
OL,16,Fneedless grief and pain following
OL,17,Fdeath and injury during childbirth".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FJack and Sarah Hawkins were one of the
OL,8,Ffirst families to raise concerns about
OL,9,Fthe Nottingham University Hospitals
OL,10,FNHS trust after they lost their
OL,11,Fdaughter, Harriet, during labour in
OL,12,FApril 2016.
OL,14,FBut so many women wanted to share
OL,15,Ftheir stories when the inquiry opened
OL,16,Fthat it became the largest maternity
OL,17,Freview in NHS history.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FWomen frequently reported invasive
OL,8,Fprocedures were forced upon them or
OL,9,Fperformed entirely without their
OL,10,Fknowledge or consent.
OL,12,FOne woman, who was at the hospital in
OL,13,F2019, said: "Despite having a document
OL,14,Fthat detailed my preferences, during
OL,15,Fmy stay at City Hospital, I felt
OL,16,Fcoerced to accept an oxytocin drip,
OL,17,Fboth things I had researched and knew
OL,18,FI didn't want, having looked into the
OL,19,Fevidence behind them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"I agreed to an internal examination,
OL,8,Fbut during this exam, the midwife
OL,9,Fperformed a membrane sweep without
OL,10,Fnotice or consent."
OL,12,FAnother said: "My waters were broken
OL,13,Fagainst my will."
OL,26,@uD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FOne mother said her pain was ignored
OL,8,Fand diminished: "They were very
OL,9,Fdismissive... 'is this your first
OL,10,Fbaby?'... take some paracetamol... and
OL,11,Fhave a hot bath... and the only way we
OL,12,Fwent to hospital was by just not even
OL,13,Flistening to them...we just turned
OL,14,Fup..."
OL,16,FOthers felt disrespected by staff,
OL,17,Fsaying: "The midwife told my partner
OL,18,Fto put his hand over my mouth."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FAs recently as 2020, one mother said
OL,8,Fshe wasn't believed by staff about her
OL,9,Fpain "...they then spent 12 hours not
OL,10,Fbelieving me that I was in labour,
OL,11,Fdenying me of pain relief, leaving me
OL,12,Fcompletely alone with no partner
OL,13,Fthroughout, on a ward, not conducting
OL,14,Fadequate checks, lying in my medical
OL,15,Fnotes to cover their backs....and then
OL,16,Fdid not openly and honestly
OL,17,Finvestigate my complaint".
OL,19,FSome mothers left the hospital in
OL,20,Fterror at the idea of ever having to
OL,21,Fgive birth again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FOne told the review about her
OL,8,Fexperience in 2014, "When I discovered
OL,9,FI was pregnant with my second child,
OL,10,Fmy immediate reaction was to terminate
OL,11,Fthe pregnancy because I was too
OL,12,Ffrightened to go through the
OL,13,Fexperience I did with my
OL,14,Fdaughter...Having been desperate to
OL,15,Fhave any children this speaks volumes
OL,16,Fabout the level of trauma..."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThis review found that none of these
OL,8,Fincidents was an isolated incident but
OL,9,Finstead part of a wider culture that
OL,10,Ftreated women with contempt,
OL,11,Fsummarising it as consistent "breaches
OL,12,Fof fundamental standards of dignity,
OL,13,Frespect, and professionalism."
OL,15,FWhat the Trust says
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FAnthony May, CEO at Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust (NUH),
OL,9,Fsaid: "I want to pay tribute to the
OL,10,Fbravery of the many families who have
OL,11,Fworked tirelessly to get answers and
OL,12,Fto make maternity services safer for
OL,13,Fothers.
OL,15,F"They have campaigned tirelessly and
OL,16,Fdeserve a great deal of credit for
OL,17,Fwhat they have done to improve
OL,18,Fmaternity safety.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"I have met some of the affected
OL,8,Ffamilies, and they have shared their
OL,9,Fpainful and life-changing experiences
OL,10,Fwith me, for which I am very grateful.
OL,12,F"I am very sorry for the pain and
OL,13,Fsuffering these families have endured.
OL,15,F"It is from my conversations with
OL,16,Faffected families that I understand
OL,17,Fhow important and significant this
OL,18,Fperiod is for them, as they await the
OL,19,Foutcome of Donna Ockenden's review. I
OL,20,Fhope they receive the answers they
OL,21,Fhave been waiting so long for."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34520
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"Upon receiving the findings of the
OL,8,Freview, we will consider carefully
OL,9,Fwhat we need to do next to ensure that
OL,10,Fwe learn from what happened in the
OL,11,Fpast and to continue to improve
OL,12,Fmaternity services."
OL,14,FThis report has a big aim - to change
OL,15,Fmaternity care across the country.
OL,17,FThis report provides a number of
OL,18,Fessential recommendations for both NUH
OL,19,Fand national maternity care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G20/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34521
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FLocally, the report calls for improved
OL,8,Fstaff training, empowering them to
OL,9,Ffeel confident speaking up about
OL,10,Fissues, and better monitoring of
OL,11,Fbabies to ensure interventions are
OL,12,Fmade quickly.
OL,14,FStaff need clear pathways to report
OL,15,Ftheir concerns and get them seen at
OL,16,Fthe highest level.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G21/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34522
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FIt also recommends more psychological
OL,8,Fsupport for families after traumatic
OL,9,Fbirths, and ensuring that all families
OL,10,Fare involved in investigations into
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FIt calls for improvements in
OL,14,Fleadership, culture, training, and
OL,15,Foverall maternity care at the NUH.
OL,17,FThe report also looks more broadly at
OL,18,Fnational maternity care and offers a
OL,19,Fnumber of recommendations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G22/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34523
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FImplement Martha's Rule: This report
OL,8,Frecommends rolling it out to all
OL,9,Fmaternity departments across the
OL,10,Fcountry. The rule gives patients and
OL,11,Ffamilies the right to request a rapid
OL,12,Freview if they are concerned about a
OL,13,Fcondition worsening. It gives families
OL,14,Fformal access to a team which can give
OL,15,Fa second opinion.
OL,17,FThe government has committed to this
OL,18,Ffollowing the review.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G23/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34524
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FOverall, the report calls for women to
OL,8,Fbe listened to, saying "women must be
OL,9,Fat the centre of clinical
OL,10,Fcommunication and informed decision-
OL,11,Fmaking"
OL,13,FStaffing and culture change: The
OL,14,Freport recommends investing in
OL,15,Fstaffing to ensure all maternity and
OL,16,Fneonatal units meet standards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G24/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34525
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FThe report also calls for action to
OL,8,Fend bullying of both patients and
OL,9,Ffrontline staff. Bullying came up in
OL,10,Fthe survey, but the report highlights
OL,11,Fthat the issue extends far beyond NUH.
OL,13,F"A 2025 survey by the Nursing and
OL,14,FMidwifery Council found that 70% of
OL,15,Frespondents reported bullying or
OL,16,Fharassment, with almost a third
OL,17,Fwitnessing situations where patient
OL,18,Fsafety or care was compromised."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G25/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34526
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FImprove leadership and oversight:
OL,8,FMaternity care should be prioritised
OL,9,Fby senior leaders. The report says
OL,10,Fthat Maternity did not feature as an
OL,11,Fitem on the Trust Board "in any
OL,12,Fsubstantive way until 2020".
OL,14,FAlongside increased formal scrutiny,
OL,15,Fthe report emphasises the need for a
OL,16,Fcultural shift at the top, stating
OL,17,Fthat "true excellence relies on
OL,18,Fempathetic leadership, individualised
OL,19,Fcare, and an unwavering commitment to
OL,20,Fsystemic equity."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G26/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34527
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FIt also calls for more training to be
OL,8,Fgiven to anyone involved with
OL,9,Fmaternity care and regular risk
OL,10,Fassessments of women through pregnancy.
OL,12,FDonna Ockenden, Chair of the
OL,13,FIndependent Review, said: "Today, the
OL,14,FIndependent Review into Maternity
OL,15,FServices at Nottingham University
OL,16,FHospitals NHS Trust has published its
OL,17,Ffindings, conclusions and actions.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G27/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34528
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FFirst and foremost, the Review Team
OL,8,Fand I would like to express our
OL,9,Fdeepest gratitude to the thousands of
OL,10,Ffamilies, staff and community
OL,11,Frepresentatives who placed their trust
OL,12,Fin us and contributed to this Review.
OL,14,F"Many shared the most painful chapters
OL,15,Fof their lives, speaking with
OL,16,Fextraordinary courage about
OL,17,Fexperiences of trauma and grief. They
OL,18,Fdid so not only in pursuit of answers
OL,19,Ffor themselves, but in the hope that
OL,20,Fno other family would have to endure
OL,21,Fwhat they have experienced.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G28/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34529
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"To every family who came forward, I
OL,8,Fwant to say this: we have listened. It
OL,9,Fis my sincere hope that through this
OL,10,FReview you now feel as though your
OL,11,Fvoices have been heard and what
OL,12,Fhappened to you and your families has
OL,13,Fbeen recognised and will be acted upon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G29/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34530
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"This Review has been ongoing for more
OL,8,Fthan three years. For many families,
OL,9,Fhowever, the journey began long before
OL,10,Fthat. Some have carried the burden of
OL,11,Funanswered questions and compounded
OL,12,Fharm for more than a decade. We
OL,13,Frecognise the emotional toll that this
OL,14,Fprocess has taken on families and
OL,15,Fstaff alike.
OL,17,F"Today, we have started the process of
OL,18,Fproviding answers. We have set out
OL,19,Fclear findings and essential actions
OL,20,Fto address the concerns raised by
OL,21,Ffamilies and staff.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G30/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34531
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"These actions when implemented will
OL,8,Fdrive improvement both within
OL,9,Fperinatal services at Nottingham
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust and
OL,11,Facross England.
OL,13,F"The evidence heard by the Review Team
OL,14,Fmakes clear that we are not yet
OL,15,Fconsistently providing safe, equitable
OL,16,Fand compassionate care to all women,
OL,17,Fbabies and families. That must change.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G31/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34532
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"The Trust faces a significant journey
OL,8,Fof improvement ahead. However, it is
OL,9,Fimportant to acknowledge that progress
OL,10,Fhas already begun. The Review Team has
OL,11,Fnot waited until publication to raise
OL,12,Fconcerns or recommend action.
OL,14,F"Since September 2022, the Trust has
OL,15,Fworked closely with the Review Team to
OL,16,Flisten, learn and implement necessary
OL,17,Fchanges. While there is much more to
OL,18,Fdo, important foundations have been
OL,19,Flaid.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G32/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34533
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"As the Chief Executive of Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust,
OL,9,FAnthony May, confirmed to families in
OL,10,FMay 2026, the Review Team and I will
OL,11,Fcontinue to oversee the Trust's
OL,12,Fimprovement programme for the next two
OL,13,Fyears. This level of ongoing oversight
OL,14,Fis unique to this Review.
OL,16,F"It reflects both the scale of the
OL,17,Fissues identified and the need to
OL,18,Fprovide assurance to families, staff
OL,19,Fand the wider community that the
OL,20,Factions set out today will lead to
OL,21,Fmeaningful and lasting change.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G33/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34534
SC,0034
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,FTo those who have feared that this
OL,8,Freport might become another document
OL,9,Fon a shelf, I want to be clear: it
OL,10,Fwill not. The findings published today
OL,11,Fmust be the catalyst for safer care,
OL,12,Fgreater accountability and lasting
OL,13,Fimprovement.
OL,15,F"The families of Nottinghamshire, the
OL,16,Fstaff of the Trust, and the wider
OL,17,Fcommunities it serves have my personal
OL,18,Fand unwavering commitment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G34/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34535
SC,0035
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We owe it to those whose lives have
OL,8,Fbeen forever changed to ensure that
OL,9,Flessons are learned, improvements are
OL,10,Fdelivered, and that future families
OL,11,Freceive the safe and compassionate
OL,12,Fcare they deserve."
OL,14,FIn a statement responding to the
OL,15,Freview, the Nottingham University
OL,16,FHospital NHS Trust said, "Today,
OL,17,FWednesday 24 June, the findings from
OL,18,Fthe Independent Maternity Review (IMR)
OL,19,Finto services at Nottingham University
OL,20,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) were
OL,21,Fpublished.
OL,26,@tD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G35/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34536
SC,0036
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"The Review, led by Donna Ockenden,
OL,8,Foutlines how, where and why care in
OL,9,Four services had resulted in harm to
OL,10,Fmothers and babies in their hospitals
OL,11,Fand made recommendations of actions to
OL,12,Fimprove care in the future.
OL,14,F"Wefullyaccept thefindings of the
OL,15,FReview andtake responsibility for the
OL,16,Ffailings that are detailed within it.
OL,17,FAn initial response to the review,
OL,18,Fshared by Chief Executive Anthony May
OL,19,Fand Trust Chair Nick Carver, follows.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G36/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34537
SC,0037
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We will now take time to carefully
OL,8,Fconsider and reflect further on the
OL,9,FReview outcomes and its
OL,10,Frecommendations."
OL,12,FThey've also written an open letter to
OL,13,Fthe people of Nottinghamshire:
OL,15,F"The publication of the independent
OL,16,Freview into maternity services in
OL,17,FNottingham is a watershed moment for
OL,18,Faffected families, our staff and for
OL,19,Fthe communities we serve.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G37/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34538
SC,0038
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We apologise unreservedly to the
OL,8,Fwomen and families who have suffered
OL,9,Fharm, loss, trauma or distress while
OL,10,Freceiving care in our services. We
OL,11,Ffailed you, and on behalf of
OL,12,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust,
OL,13,Fwe accept responsibility for our
OL,14,Ffailings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G38/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34539
SC,0039
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"Many families have been generous
OL,8,Fenough to meet with us, showing
OL,9,Fextraordinary courage and
OL,10,Fdetermination. We are grateful for
OL,11,Fthat, and we want you to know that the
OL,12,Fpublication of this report is not the
OL,13,Fend of a process. It is another
OL,14,Fimportant milestone in a journey that
OL,15,Fmust continue. Your bravery and
OL,16,Fcommitment to speaking up is helping
OL,17,Fimprove maternity care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G39/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34540
SC,0040
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We want to thank Donna Ockenden for
OL,8,Fher work and for engaging with us
OL,9,Fthroughout this process. Donna's
OL,10,Freview has provided an opportunity to
OL,11,Fhear directly from thousands of
OL,12,Ffamilies and staff. The direct
OL,13,Ffeedback we have had throughout has
OL,14,Fhelped us with our improvement
OL,15,Fefforts. As a result, whilst there is
OL,16,Fmore to do, important changes have
OL,17,Fbeen made and we believe our services
OL,18,Fare now safer, kinder and better led.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G40/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34541
SC,0041
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We recognise that trust is earned
OL,8,Fthrough actions, not words. We know,
OL,9,Falso, that families and the wider
OL,10,Fpublic will judge us not by what we
OL,11,Fsay today, but by what we do next.
OL,13,F"The review makes clear that while
OL,14,Fimprovements have been made, there is
OL,15,Fstill more to do. We will take time to
OL,16,Freflect on the report with humility,
OL,17,Fhonesty and determination.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G41/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34542
SC,0042
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"At the same time, we will work with
OL,8,Ffamilies on a meaningful apology
OL,9,Fbecause we know it is important to
OL,10,Fthem that this is reflective of the
OL,11,Ffindings of the review, and our
OL,12,Fcommitment to lasting improvement. We
OL,13,Fcan say with certainty that families
OL,14,Fwill continue to be involved in our
OL,15,Fimprovement plans because this review
OL,16,Fhas proved that we can learn from them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G42/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
