OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34543
SC,0043
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We must also acknowledge our staff.
OL,8,FEvery day we see dedicated,
OL,9,Fcompassionate professionals working
OL,10,Ftirelessly to provide the best
OL,11,Fpossible care for women and families,
OL,12,Foften under extreme pressure and
OL,13,Fscrutiny.
OL,15,F"Whilst the publication of the report
OL,16,Fwill be difficult for them too, we
OL,17,Fknow they will reflect on the findings
OL,18,Fof the review and see this as an
OL,19,Fopportunity to continue our
OL,20,Fimprovement journey.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G43/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34544
SC,0044
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"To these colleagues, we want to say
OL,8,Fthat we know that we did not always
OL,9,Fprovide you with the right conditions
OL,10,Fto do your jobs as you would wish and
OL,11,Fwe take responsibility for that.
OL,13,F"At Nottingham University Hospitals,
OL,14,Fwe are determined to provide maternity
OL,15,Fservices that are consistently safe,
OL,16,Fcompassionate, equitable and
OL,17,Fresponsive.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G44/45
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34545
SC,0045
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782370082
OL,3,C500 mothers and babies 'died or
OL,4,Csuffered avoidable harm', damning
OL,5,Creport reveals
OL,7,F"We want every family to have
OL,8,Fconfidence in the care they receive.
OL,9,FWe want to reassure anyone using our
OL,10,Fservices today that you will be safe
OL,11,Fin our care.
OL,13,F"On behalf of the Trust, we renew the
OL,14,Fcommitments to transparency, openness
OL,15,Fand accountability. Most importantly,
OL,16,Fwe renew our commitment to providing
OL,17,Fsafe, high-quality maternity care at
OL,18,Fyour hospitals."
OL,20,FSupport and advice available for
OL,21,Fparents and families:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G45/45
